detailed.description:
Doen Peony Ruffle Dress in Salt White Romantic Boho Fairy Womens Small

This gorgeous “salt white” mini dress deserves to be worn on an ice cream date or to frolic in a field. It’s fun, it’s flirtatious, it’s romantic. 

Made with Ramie fabric, also known as grass linen - a natural, sustainable, renewable material that comes from the nettle plant family. It's perfect for warm and humid climates - soft to the touch and breathable, sweat and moisture wicking, strong even when wet, dries quickly, and naturally resistant to stains, bacteria, and shrinkage.

An asymmetrical button front framed with picot-edged ruffles and pintucks makes a dreamy combination. Shoulder snaps and an adjustable tie-waist allow for easy on-off and personalized fit.

Armpit-armpit: 17.75”
Length: 33”

Pictured on Emily Schuman of “Cupcakes and Cashmere” and waiting to be worn to your next garden party.
